.TH AUDITAI 1 "June 2026" "auditai 1.0.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
auditai \- assess Linux host vulnerability and hardening posture
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B auditai
.RI [ options ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
AuditAI runs local Linux security scanners and creates HTML or Markdown
reports. AI synthesis is optional.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-\-no-ai
Run scanners and create reports without an AI API key.
.TP
.BR \-\-modules " " LIST
Run a comma-separated subset of scanner modules.
.TP
.BR \-\-skip " " LIST
Skip comma-separated scanner modules.
.TP
.BR \-\-output-dir " " DIR
Write reports to DIR.
.SH EXAMPLE
.B sudo auditai --no-ai --output-dir ./output
